[FW03A2Install.HW]
AddReg=Dev_AddRegFW03A2

[FW03A3Install.HW]
AddReg=Dev_AddRegFW03A3


[Dev_AddRegFW01A1]
HKR,,DeviceInterfaceGUIDs,0x10000,"{57baa63d-5e5a-42f5-8ce5-eaf78b45bacf}"

[Dev_AddRegFW01A2]
